      "@type": "pm:Bridge",
      "stableId": "bridge.block_average_coercivity",
      "name": "Block-average mass term as a coercivity bridge",
      "description": "A block Poincare estimate turns a nonnegative kinetic operator K plus a positive term a Q†Q into a coercive precision with lower bound min(1,a)/C_P. The abstract lemma isolates the model-specific task of proving the gauge block estimate.",
