      "@type": "pm:Bridge",
      "stableId": "bridge.cluster_expansion_with_holes",
      "name": "Cluster expansion with holes and active skeletons",
      "description": "Transforms raw local activities into renormalized polymer activities by connected Mayer covers, ultralocal integration and a second Ursell expansion. The active skeleton controls connectivity and incompatibility, while the full target controls union and locality.",
