      "@id": "https://lluiseriksson.github.io/physmath-knowledge-tree/id/bridge.gaussian_precision_markov_blanket",
      "@type": "pm:Bridge",
      "stableId": "bridge.gaussian_precision_markov_blanket",
      "name": "Sparse Gaussian precision as an exact Markov blanket",
      "description": "For a nondegenerate finite Gaussian split into interior, collar and exterior variables, a zero interior–exterior block in the precision matrix implies exact conditional factorization of interior and exterior given the collar. Decay of inverse diagonal blocks then bounds how collar values influence conditional means.",
